        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 7. Specimen (R 20 mm) of Astropecten marginatus Gray, 1840 (MZUSP 2100): (A) abactinal and (B) actinal view of body; (C) proximal paxillae; (D) madreporite; (E) ambulacral furrow (proximal region on the right); (F) actinal view of inferomarginal plates (proximal region to the left); (G) terminal region of the arm showing terminal plate; and (H) oral region. Scale bars: A–B, 10 mm; C–H, 1 mm." ;
